===Noun===
'''rest''' (''uncountable'')

# {{physics}} [[State]] of no [[motion]].
# (''people'') State of [[quiet]] and [[recreation]].
# That which [[remains]].
#:''She ate a little bit and put the '''rest''' in the fridge for later.''

